~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
                 O F F W I E L D
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Usage:	offwield <weapon>
	
Description: 	This is the highest of the 
		fighting skills taught in 
		the Dark Order, reserved 
		for those who master the
		teachings of the guild.  
		It allows you to wield a
		second weapon during 
		combat.  Obviously, the
		weapon you wield and 
		offwield must not be a 
		two-handed weapon.
	
Minimum Guild Level: 8

Minimum Game Level: 19

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

